The paper discusses a methodology for optimizing the efficiency and robustness of deep learning models through quantization. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), as well as computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also involves image classification tasks (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.NE.
